LANGUAGE "SIC 1.0".
SCROLL STRONG scribe_scroll
MODE CHANT.
PROFILE "CIVIL"


WORK MAIN WITH SIGIL UNUSED AS TEXT:
    SAY: "Entering SCRIBE demo.".

    LET SIGIL name BE "SIC".
    LET SIGIL realm BE "Empire of Languages".

    SCRIBE: "In the annals of " + realm + ", " + name + " awakens.".
    LOG: "Raw sigil dump: " + name + " / " + realm + ".".

    THUS WE ANSWER WITH "SCRIBE demo complete.".
ENDWORK
